                <h1>Understanding Texas Background Check Laws</h1>
                <p>Texas background check laws regulate the process of collecting and using personal information for employment, housing, and firearm purchases. Employers must obtain consent before conducting checks, and individuals have the right to review their information. Awareness of local regulations is essential for compliance and protecting privacy.</p>
